<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(بَاب الشين)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٧٤٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شُرَيْح:</span> الْخُزَاعِيّ، خويلد بن<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَمْرو الكعبي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل اسْمه:</span> هَانِيء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أخبرنَا أَحْمد بن الْحسن بن عتبَة، ثَنَا عبد الله<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ابْن بحيس الْمدنِي، ثَنَا الْحزَامِي،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَأَبُو شُرَيْح الكعبي اسْمه:</span> خويلد.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣٧٤١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شُرَيْح:</span> هَانِيء بن يزِيد الْحَارِثِيّ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>كناه النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْنه شُرَيْح.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣٧٤٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شُرَيْح:</span> عبد الرَّحْمَن بن شُرَيْح<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>الإسْكَنْدراني الْمصْرِيّ، كَانَ ينزل المعافر.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عبد الله بن الْمُبَارك، وَعبد الله بن<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وهب.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٣٧٤٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شُرَيْح:</span> ضبارة بن مَالك<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>الْحِمصِي.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> بَقِيَّة، وَإِسْمَاعِيل بن عَيَّاش.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c2">(من كنيته أَبُو شَدَّاد)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٣٧٤٤ - <span class="c2">(ق ١٥٨ / أ)</span> أَبُو شَدَّاد: شهد<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَفَاة النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مُعَاوِيَة بن صَالح الْحِمصِي.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٣٧٤٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَدَّاد:</span> رجل من أهل دَمًا،<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>كتب إِلَيْهِ النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عبد الْعَزِيز بن زِيَاد.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>٣٧٤٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَدَّاد:</span> اسْمه سلمَان.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أم سَلمَة.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>كناه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>٣٧٤٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَدَّاد:</span> إِسْحَاق بن مُضر<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>الْمروزِي.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مُسلم بن الْحجَّاج.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>٣٧٤٨ - أَبُو شَدَّاد.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> مُجَاهِد.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْن جريج.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>٣٧٤٩ - أَبُو شَدَّاد.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> جَابر.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عمر بن نَبهَان.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>